data.description: This charming residence, with three bedrooms and two bathrooms, spans 2,277 square feet and occupies more than one acre of land in a horse-friendly area approved by zoning regulations. The house highlights a dining space for hosting, while the garage comes equipped with a practical workshop section. This property seamlessly combines generous living spaces with ample possibilities for equestrian activities, making it an essential visit for those in search of both relaxation and rural allure.
